# Typography System Rules

## Font Sizes and Line Heights

### Headings
- **H1 (Hero/Main Page Title)**
  ```css
  text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl /* 36px -> 48px -> 60px */
  leading-tight /* line-height: 1.25 */
  ```

- **H2 (Section Headers)**
  ```css
  text-3xl md:text-4xl /* 30px -> 36px */
  leading-tight /* line-height: 1.25 */
  mb-4 /* margin-bottom spacing */
  ```

- **H3 (Card/Component Titles)**
  ```css
  text-lg md:text-xl /* 18px -> 20px */
  leading-snug /* line-height: 1.375 */
  mb-3 /* margin-bottom spacing */
  ```

- **H4 (Subsection/Small Titles)**
  ```css
  text-lg /* 18px */
  leading-snug /* line-height: 1.375 */
  ```

### Body Text
- **Large Body**
  ```css
  text-base md:text-lg /* 16px -> 18px */
  leading-relaxed /* line-height: 1.625 */
  ```

- **Regular Body**
  ```css
  text-base /* 16px */
  leading-relaxed /* line-height: 1.625 */
  ```

- **Small Text**
  ```css
  text-sm md:text-base /* 14px -> 16px */
  leading-normal /* line-height: 1.5 */
  ```

### Special Text
- **Prices/Important Numbers**
  ```css
  text-xl md:text-2xl /* 20px -> 24px */
  font-bold
  ```

- **Labels/Tags**
  ```css
  text-sm /* 14px */
  font-medium
  ```

## Spacing Guidelines

### Vertical Rhythm
- Section spacing: `py-16 lg:py-24`
- Between major components: `mb-16`
- Between related elements: `mb-8`
- Between text elements: `mb-4` or `mb-6`
- Inside cards/components: `mb-2` or `mb-3`

### Container Widths
```css
max-w-7xl /* Maximum content width */
mx-auto /* Center content */
px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 /* Responsive padding */
```

